SELECT [s].[Id], [s].[UserId] AS [userId], [t1].[Name] AS [Grade]
FROM [Students] AS [s]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[AcademicGradeClassId], [a].[StudentId]
    FROM [AcademicStudents] AS [a]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t] ON [s].[Id] = [t].[StudentId]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[GradeId]
    FROM [AcademicGradeClasses] AS [a0]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a0].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t0] ON [t].[AcademicGradeClassId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [g].[Id], [g].[Name]
    FROM [Grades] AS [g]
    WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_3 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([g].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))
) AS [t1] ON [t0].[GradeId] = [t1].[Id]
WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([s].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND [s].[UserId] IS NULL

) AS [t] ON [s].[UserId] = [t].[Id]

    SELECT [a0].[AcademicGradeClassId], [a0].[StudentId]
    FROM [AcademicStudents] AS [a0]

) AS [t0] ON [s].[Id] = [t0].[StudentId]

) AS [t1] ON [t0].[AcademicGradeClassId] = [t1].[Id]

) AS [t2] ON [t1].[GradeId] = [t2].[Id]

) AS [t] ON [s].[UserId] = [t].[Id]

INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[Name]
    FROM [AbpUsers] AS [a]
    WHERE ((@__ef_filter__p_1 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([a].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))) AND ((@__ef_filter__p_2 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR [a].[TenantId] IS NULL)
) AS [t] ON ((COALESCE([s].[Name], N'') + CAST(N' ' AS nvarchar(max))) + COALESCE([s].[FamilyName], N'')) = [t].[Name]
WHERE (@__ef_filter__p_0 = CAST(1 AS bit)) OR ([s].[IsDeleted] <> CAST(1 AS bit))

        SELECT 1
        FROM [Students] AS [s]
        INNER JOIN (
